      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5803604/" class="title-link">历史的记忆需要公开公正的理性探究</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5803604"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
